## Technical

- PHP, with the [Kohana](http://kohanaframework.org/) framework
- Supports MySQL and PDO databases
  - In turn, [PDO supports](http://www.php.net/manual/en/pdo.drivers.php)
    - MySQL
    - PostgreSQL
    - SQLite
    - Oracle
    - ODBC and DB2
    - 4D
    - MS SQL
    - CUBRID
    - Informix
    - Firebird
    - IBM

